Javascript

scrolltTo automatically scrolls to a preset location

Here, it set itself to scrollTo(0, 0);
0,0 are X Y coordinates

Increase count by interval
const timer = setInterval(() => {
result.querySelector('span').textContent = `${output}%`;
if(output === score){
clearInterval(timer);
} else {
output++;
}
}, 10);
